Old North Capital Investments, LLC $50,000,000 Financing
Old North Capital Investments, LLC just submitted form D announcing $50,000,000 financing.  This is a new filing. Old North Capital Investments, LLC was able to sell $500,000. That is 1% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $50,000,000. The financing was made by 1 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $10,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-09. Old North Capital Investments, LLC is based in  525 N TRYON STREET SUITE 1600 CHARLOTTE 28202. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  David Seroy.





