OUR SERVICES




Many of our clients have relied on their employer-sponsored retirement plan, a broker or other financial product salesman, or even their own research to manage their assets. As their wealth grows and their situation changes a disciplined program of planning, managing and investing their assets becomes important.
Old North Advisors provides comprehensive wealth management that takes into consideration all aspects of the client's financial situation.  Our investment advisory process is rigorous, dispassionate, rooted in research - and disciplined.  Our account management and reporting services are timely, thorough and user friendly.
Our specific services include:

Customized investment strategies
Financial planning and advice in a wide range of areas
Investment policy development for foundations and endowments
Ongoing portfolio performance monitoring
Estate plan coordination and assistance
Education planning

Old North Advisors investment services are discretionary, which means that you do not have to give approval of every trade and transaction.  However, every investment decision made on your behalf adheres to your investment*policy*statement and information preferences and will be communicated to you in a timely manner.




"

                   At some point, professional planning and management makes sense for most investors.                 
